{"tid":1866504,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"天滅CCTVB 愛回家劉丹發燒停工 未知是否中左武肺","createTime":"2020-02-06T18:43:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T19:49:50.000Z","uid":171273,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"635d7750af2290f0a924d7a3eed8caadf0e31472","tid":1866504,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:43:31.000Z","msg":"爆劉丹發燒兼咳嗽<br />\n滕麗名又指現在不能夠大笑，因大笑會感到痛楚，今日要與周嘉洛拍「床戲」昨晚也吃定醫生開的嗎啡止痛藥。問到是否要追拍進度，她說：「原本我未開工，但係因為丹爺（劉丹）病咗，發燒、咳嗽，要9我號先開工，佢哋問我得唔得，所以我就提早開工。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200206/mobile/bkn-20200206140031040-0206_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200206%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200206140031040-0206_00862_001.html&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWd%2BR0LtvndqJ8lr%2BzYsHiyM%3D&h=23277fde\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200206/mobile/bkn-20200206140031040-0206_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"63ee7395480e1dadedca1cdfafaa939f09041540","tid":1866504,"uid":171273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:44:03.000Z","msg":"比左錢CCTVB 8點廣告時段自己執生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eff781cacde2a9ad81e34fa3de3055c586f74b5","tid":1866504,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:49:25.000Z","msg":"<em><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></em>"},{"pid":"ceeeef8f2de9dfe66a7a3af73270ed3d7934ae6e","tid":1866504,"uid":171273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b576cebcfc74933efd12282cbd75a22fa5e85a9d","tid":1866504,"uid":30836,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T18:56:52.000Z","msg":"屌我記得之前有人開咗個po<br />\n問TVB開套以武漢肺炎為主題嘅劇會叫咩名<br />\n<br />\n依稀記得有個巴打話咩 愛回家之肺炎速遞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/